  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/CoreWLAN\/CWPHYMode\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T14:35:07Z\n---\n\n# CWPHYMode\n\n**Enumeration**\n\nCoreWLAN physical layer modes.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nenum CWPHYMode\n```\n\n## Constants\n\n- **CWPHYMode.modeNone**: No specified mode.\n- **CWPHYMode.mode11a**: IEEE 802.11a PHY.\n- **CWPHYMode.mode11b**: IEEE 802.11b PHY.\n- **CWPHYMode.mode11g**: IEEE 802.11g PHY.\n- **CWPHYMode.mode11n**: IEEE 802.11n PHY.\n- **CWPHYMode.mode11ac**: IEEE 802.11ac PHY.\n\n## Enumeration Cases\n\n- **CWPHYMode.mode11ax**\n- **CWPHYMode.mode11be**\n\n## Initializers\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Enumerations\n\n- **CWChannelBand**: CoreWLAN channel bands.\n- **CWChannelWidth**: CoreWLAN channel widths.\n- **CWCipherKeyFlags**: Cipher key flags.\n- **CWErr**\n- **CWEventType**: Wi-Fi event types.\n- **CWIBSSModeSecurity**: IBSS mode security types.\n- **CWInterfaceMode**: Wi-Fi interface operating modes.\n- **CWKeychainDomain**: Keychain domain types that CoreWLAN keychain methods use.\n- **CWSecurity**: CoreWLAN security types.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- BitwiseCopyable\n- Equatable\n- Hashable\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
